<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include ("../partials/head") %>
  </head>

  <header>
    <%- include ("../partials/header") %>
  </header>

  <main>
    <style>
      html,
      /* body {
        overflow: hidden;
      } */

      html {
        height: 100%;
      }

      body {
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(249, 195, 71, 1) 0%, rgba(243, 110, 127, 1) 100%);
      }

      .container {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        -moz-transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
        -webkit-transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
      }

      .success {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        line-height: 35px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        background: rgb(167, 29, 185);
        transition: all 0.1s ease 0s;
        border: 0;
        padding-left: 2em;
        padding-right: 2em;
        /* letter-spacing: -0.05em; */
      }

      .btn-success:hover {
        background: rgb(107, 0, 194);
      }

      .info {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        line-height: 35px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        background: rgb(58, 149, 202);
        transition: all 0.1s ease 0s;
        border: 0;
        padding-left: 2em;
        padding-right: 2em;
      }

      .btn-info:hover {
        background: rgb(1, 108, 170);
      }

      .flex {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
      }

      form {
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      input {
        float: right;
        clear: both;
      }

      .circle-small {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(243, 110, 127, 1) 0%, rgba(249, 195, 71, 1) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        height: 15em;
        width: 15em;
        position: fixed;
        left: 200px;
        top: 100px;
      }

      .circle-medium {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(243, 110, 127, 1) 0%, rgba(249, 195, 71, 1) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        height: 35em;
        width: 35em;
        position: fixed;
        left: 1000px;
        top: 200px;
      }

      .circle-medium2 {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(243, 110, 127, 1) 0%, rgba(249, 195, 71, 1) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        height: 35em;
        width: 35em;
        position: fixed;
        left: 1200px;
        top: 620px;
      }

      .circle-large {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(243, 110, 127, 1) 0%, rgba(249, 195, 71, 1) 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        height: 55em;
        width: 55em;
        position: fixed;
        left: 200px;
        top: 300px;
      }
    </style>

    <body>
      <header id="header" class="fixed-top" style="padding-top: 3.8em;">
        <div class="container d-flex align-items-center">
          <a href="/" class="logo mr-auto"> <img src="assets/img/logo.png" alt="" class="img-fluid" /></a>

          <nav class="nav-menu d-none d-lg-block">
            <ul>
              <li>
                <a href="/" style="font-family: gotham-medium;">Home</a>
              </li>
              <li class="active">
                <a href="/about" style="font-family: gotham-medium;">About</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/legal" style="font-family: gotham-medium;">Legal</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
          <!-- .nav-menu -->
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="bgimage text-left">
        <p class="circle-medium"></p>
        <p class="circle-medium2"></p>
        <p class="circle-large"></p>
        <p class="circle-small"></p>
        <div id="host" class="container container-fluid" style="color: white;">
          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading" style="font-family: gotham; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            About:
          </h1>
          <p class="lead" style="font-family: gotham-medium; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">
            Listen Along is a website meant to let groups to connect in a way that people have been for hundreds of years, through music.
            <br />
            Using the software and power of Spotify, Listen Along allows groups of people to listen to a specific host's music for as long as they want.
          </p>
          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading" style="font-family: gotham; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            FAQ:
          </h1>
          <p class="lead" style="font-family: gotham-medium; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">
            Q: What are the site restrictions?
            <br />
            A: To HOST a Spotify music party, you can be premium or non-premium Spotify user.
            <br />
            A: To JOIN to a Spotify music party, you MUST be a Spotify Premium user.
            <br />
            <br />
            Q: Why can't I hear any music after I input the host code?
            <br />
            A: Make sure that you have your Spotify app open, in some cases you should also listen to random music so that the website knows which device is active.
            <br />
            <br />
            Q: How many people can join a music party?
            <br />
            A: Unlimited users can join! Or until Spotify starts rate limiting this website... ðŸ¤”
            <br />
            <br />
            Q: Does the host code ever expire?
            <br />
            A: No, the host can invalidate their code by pressing the 'Stop Party' button.
            <br />
            <br />
            Q: Where can I report bugs or submit feature requests?
            <br />
            A: You can message me on
            <a href="https://twitter.com/RoaringIron" style="color: #2a2a72;" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
            about anything related to Listen Along!
          </p>

          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading" style="font-family: gotham; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Socials:
          </h1>
          <p class="lead" style="font-family: gotham-medium; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">
            You can follow me on social media to stay updated on new features:
            <br />
            Twitter:
            <a href="https://twitter.com/RoaringIron" style="color: #2a2a72;" target="_blank">@roaringiron</a>
            <br />
            Website:
            <a href="https://roaringiron.com" style="color: #2a2a72;" target="_blank">https://roaringiron.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </body>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <%- include ("../partials/footer") %>
  </footer>
</html>
